=begin pod
=head2 get-deltas

Extracts delta information from a touchpad event.

=begin code
method get-deltas ( Num() $dx, Num() $dy )
=end code

=item $dx; (transfer ownership: full) return location for x.
=item $dy; (transfer ownership: full) return location for y.

